    "body": "The pony_language_server has been moved into the main ponyc repository and has been called `pony-lsp` in there https://github.com/ponylang/ponyc/tree/main/tools/pony-lsp\r\n\r\nThis PR adapts the lspconfig entry to the same effect. It is considered less confusing for people to find the pony-lsp under `pony_lsp`, rather than `pony_language_server`",
